OL,3,CWelsh government accepts 'need' to
OL,4,Cimprove guidance on teaching reading
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has admitted that
OL,7,Fit needs to clarify its guidance for
OL,8,Fschools on how to teach reading.
OL,10,FThis is in response to an ITV News
OL,11,Finvestigation which revealed that
OL,12,Fmethods of teaching reading which have
OL,13,Fbeen discredited for decades are being
OL,14,Fused across Wales.
