OL,3,CWelsh government accepts 'need' to
OL,4,Cimprove guidance on teaching reading
OL,6,FITV News analysed hundreds of primary
OL,7,Fschool inspection reports, school
OL,8,Fwebsites, and teaching resources and
OL,9,Ffound that primary schools are using a
OL,10,Fmethod commonly referred to as
OL,11,F"cueing" to teach children to tackle
OL,12,Funfamiliar words alongside phonics.
OL,14,FThis method has been proven to make it
OL,15,Fmore difficult for some children to
OL,16,Flearn to read but our investigation
OL,17,Ffound its use is being praised by
OL,18,Fschool inspectors.
