OL,4,Cimprove guidance on teaching reading
OL,6,FA method known as Systematic Synthetic
OL,7,FPhonics - where children are taught to
OL,8,Fsay the sounds represented by a letter
OL,9,For letter group and blend them into
OL,10,Fwords - was implemented in England by
OL,11,Fthe last Labour government in 2005,
OL,12,Fbut the Welsh government opted not to
OL,13,Ffollow suit.
