OL,3,CWelsh government accepts 'need' to
OL,4,Cimprove guidance on teaching reading
OL,6,FYesterday, when being questioned
OL,7,Frepeatedly in the Senedd about ITV
OL,8,FNews' investigation, the Cabinet
OL,9,FSecretary for Education, Lynne Neagle,
OL,10,Fclaimed that the government has a
OL,11,F"clear expectation that all schools
OL,12,Fwill use synthetic phonics to teach
OL,13,Freading."
