OL,3,CWelsh government accepts 'need' to
OL,4,Cimprove guidance on teaching reading
OL,6,FResponding to a call on the government
OL,7,Fto mandate the teaching of Systematic
OL,8,FSynthetic Phonics, the civil servant
OL,9,Freplied that "to impose one method of
OL,10,Fteaching phonics on schools would
OL,11,Fundermine the Curriculum for Wales
OL,12,Fframework which is inclusive of all
OL,13,Flearners and designed to support
OL,14,Fschools design their own curriculum..."
