OL,3,CWelsh government accepts 'need' to
OL,4,Cimprove guidance on teaching reading
OL,6,FLast week, the Welsh government said
OL,7,Fthat it did "not advocate any one
OL,8,Fspecific method to teach reading,
OL,9,Frather we enable teachers to use their
OL,10,Fprofessional judgement and knowledge
OL,11,Fof their learners to use the best tool
OL,12,Fto meet the individual needs of their
OL,13,Flearners."
OL,15,FTonight however, a Welsh Government
OL,16,Fspokesperson said:
OL,18,F"The Cabinet Secretary's comments in
OL,19,Fthe Senedd are consistent with the
OL,20,Fdescription of phonics in our guidance
OL,21,Fon the Curriculum.
