OL,6,F"We are always interested in finding
OL,7,Fways in which we can further improve
OL,8,Four teaching methods in the best
OL,9,Finterests of children.
OL,11,F"We accept there are places in our
OL,12,Fguidance where the importance of
OL,13,Fphonics needs to be more explicit and
OL,14,Fwhere wording needs to be clarified
OL,15,Faround the use of picture cues."
OL,17,FThe schools' inspectorate Estyn has
OL,18,Fbeen approached for comment.
